{
  "stem": "15577.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, as I said, I think this was the big-- the biggest victory of-- to-- to-- to transfer the human to-- to animals.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It is the last part of my--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is last part of my career as a-- as a-- as a war inmate.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When Plaszow had to be liquidated, we-- all the time before, we knew who is Schindler.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew what he's doing for the Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We knew what an influence Schindler has on the commanding officer of Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We knew how much he could help in-- in keeping Plaszow, because there was a time when they wanted to liquidate Plaszow before and to send away all the people to death.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, owing to Schindler, or partly owing to Schindler, it was omitted.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everybody knew that if there is a paradise during this time, it is the place where Schindler has his factory.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was a group of some 300, 300, 350 people, working and living around Schindler.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He had a factory in Krakow, and he succeeded-- He was very influential.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He-- he was-- he made a lot of money during the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He got the factory from Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He sold at least half of the-- of what they made there on black market.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He made a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he knew how to bribe the right people, in the right places, in the right-- in the right time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So, he succeeded, because of all these tricks, to-- that he got the permission to settle a small camp around his factory, and to keep these 350 people around him, being affiliated, or something like this, to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That means, it was a part of Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But they, at that time, already, it was very well known that they are living like in paradise.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
